WEBVTT

00:00:00.304 --> 00:00:01.765
Understood.

00:00:02.975 --> 00:00:04.893
An unauthorized sortie
is a violation.

00:00:05.059 --> 00:00:07.728
However,
your quick and decisive action

00:00:07.730 --> 00:00:09.565
helped minimize squad casualties...

00:00:09.856 --> 00:00:14.068
and curtailed any serious harm
to the World of the Living.

00:00:14.486 --> 00:00:15.486
Therefore...

00:00:16.864 --> 00:00:19.908
I will overlook your violation
of squad rules!

00:00:20.116 --> 00:00:21.116
Yes!

00:00:21.118 --> 00:00:22.201
I mean...

00:00:22.411 --> 00:00:23.661
Thank you, sir!

00:00:24.621 --> 00:00:29.207
I'd say failing to retrieve
the remains of this mystery Hollow

00:00:29.209 --> 00:00:31.253
is a serious enough crime.

00:00:31.878 --> 00:00:32.880
By the way...

00:00:33.380 --> 00:00:37.091
Your report only describes
how unusual the Hollow was...

00:00:37.676 --> 00:00:40.887
I trust you didn't leave
anything out.

00:00:41.512 --> 00:00:46.643
That...
there was nothing else noteworthy?

00:00:51.355 --> 00:00:52.941
Yes, sir.
There wasn't anything else.

00:00:54.692 --> 00:00:57.695
JUNE 5TH, 11:00
SEITO ACADEMY HIGH SCHOOL

00:01:03.993 --> 00:01:04.912
<i>I wonder</i>

00:01:04.912 --> 00:01:07.539
<i>if that Soul Reaper made it back
to the Soul Society safely...</i>

00:01:08.165 --> 00:01:10.459
<i>I hope he's not in trouble...</i>

00:01:13.962 --> 00:01:16.590
<i>I should have at least
asked for his name.</i>

00:01:17.549 --> 00:01:20.218
THE SEIREITEI - SQUAD 10 BARRACKS

00:01:23.138 --> 00:01:28.018
<i>I guess those rumors about Quincies
still being alive were true.</i>

00:01:28.936 --> 00:01:32.438
<i>It must have taken a lot of courage
for her to save me...</i>

00:01:32.438 --> 00:01:36.484
<i>and tell me that she's a Quincy,
knowing that I'm a Soul Reaper.</i>

00:01:37.944 --> 00:01:39.195
<i>She's really something.</i>

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:42.950
<i>I should have chatted with her
a bit more.</i>

00:01:47.078 --> 00:01:50.373
Maybe I'll go back
and thank her properly this time.

00:01:52.042 --> 00:01:54.127
I told you, Ryu is my cousin!

00:01:54.377 --> 00:01:56.003
There's nothing going on
between us.

00:01:56.254 --> 00:01:59.258
You're living together,
so there <i>has</i> to be something!

00:01:59.550 --> 00:02:00.717
Come on...

00:02:02.468 --> 00:02:03.552
Huh?
H-Hey!

00:02:03.554 --> 00:02:04.638
Masaki?

00:02:05.806 --> 00:02:07.056
Oh, I-I'm sorry!

00:02:07.473 --> 00:02:09.393
Don't worry about it.

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:11.645
I hope you're okay, young lady.

00:02:13.855 --> 00:02:14.855
Are you okay?

00:02:14.856 --> 00:02:16.942
Hey! Was that a new trick
to meeting people?!

00:02:17.067 --> 00:02:19.235
Why would you think that?!

00:02:43.050 --> 00:02:47.889
<i>The blue skies above are hopelessly clear</i>

00:02:48.014 --> 00:02:53.103
<i>At my wit's end, I feel
a growing frustration</i>

00:02:53.520 --> 00:02:57.900
<i>As if to laugh at us hopeless cowards</i>

00:02:58.233 --> 00:03:01.652
<i>Countless eyes stare at us</i>

00:03:02.111 --> 00:03:07.992
<i>This soul of mine breaks again and again</i>

00:03:08.284 --> 00:03:11.205
<i>All I can do is hold it tight</i>

00:03:12.413 --> 00:03:17.461
<i>Until the day it turns to ash</i>

00:03:17.711 --> 00:03:20.338
<i>I've absorbed all of this sorrow</i>

00:03:20.463 --> 00:03:24.967
<i>It has shaped me, painted me</i>

00:03:25.092 --> 00:03:27.804
<i>But that's how we got here, right?</i>

00:03:27.930 --> 00:03:32.768
<i>One step at a time, just like breathing</i>

00:03:32.893 --> 00:03:35.270
<i>These countless scars on my palm</i>

00:03:35.395 --> 00:03:37.271
<i>That no longer fade</i>

00:03:37.396 --> 00:03:41.026
<i>Are my badge, my story</i>

00:03:41.318 --> 00:03:44.987
<i>I faced the fear and shred it to pieces</i>

00:03:45.112 --> 00:03:48.157
<i>And let it walk beside me once more</i>

00:03:48.157 --> 00:03:52.871
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:04:06.175 --> 00:04:07.216
ISHIDA RESIDENCE I'm back!

00:04:08.095 --> 00:04:09.846
- Welcome home, Masa—
- Miss Masaki.

00:04:10.389 --> 00:04:11.389
Y-Yes?

00:04:11.723 --> 00:04:12.807
I'd like a word with you.

00:04:13.934 --> 00:04:17.144
I heard you fought against
a Hollow the other night

00:04:17.144 --> 00:04:18.814
to save a Soul Reaper.

00:04:19.105 --> 00:04:20.107
Huh?

00:04:20.524 --> 00:04:23.776
No... I haven't done...
anything of the sort...

00:04:23.944 --> 00:04:26.028
You only disgrace yourself
by lying.

00:04:26.237 --> 00:04:27.238
<i>Katagiri!</i>

00:04:27.656 --> 00:04:29.324
Why did you do such a thing?

00:04:29.740 --> 00:04:31.158
Aren't you ashamed of yourself?!

00:04:31.617 --> 00:04:33.286
How could you
break the rules of the Quincies

00:04:33.286 --> 00:04:35.413
while in the care of
the Ishida Family?!

00:04:36.790 --> 00:04:37.790
Katagiri!

00:04:38.583 --> 00:04:40.002
Why did you tell Mother?!

00:04:40.584 --> 00:04:41.586
I thought I told you!

00:04:41.877 --> 00:04:43.588
That there weren't
any problems that night!

00:04:45.132 --> 00:04:47.550
But there was... a problem!

00:04:48.175 --> 00:04:49.175
What?

00:04:49.343 --> 00:04:52.848
Miss Masaki sustained a wound
from the Hollow's attack!

00:04:53.348 --> 00:04:56.600
If she doesn't get proper
Quincy treatment

00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:58.103
from your father and mother,

00:04:58.769 --> 00:05:01.271
there is a possibility
the future Ishida bloodline

00:05:01.273 --> 00:05:02.814
could become tainted!

00:05:02.815 --> 00:05:03.940
ISHIDA RESIDENCE

00:05:03.942 --> 00:05:04.276
That's nonsense!

00:05:04.651 --> 00:05:05.651
Nonsense?

00:05:06.194 --> 00:05:08.237
It means <i>everything</i> to us!

00:05:08.822 --> 00:05:10.115
You said so yourself!

00:05:10.615 --> 00:05:14.244
That your marriage to Miss Masaki
was for the future of the Quincies!

00:05:16.495 --> 00:05:17.497
Damn it!

00:05:19.458 --> 00:05:21.250
Tell me the truth!

00:05:21.500 --> 00:05:23.002
W-Well, umm...

00:05:23.002 --> 00:05:24.588
Please wait, Mother!

00:05:25.379 --> 00:05:27.548
Masaki isn't to blame
for what happened!

00:05:28.007 --> 00:05:30.427
- Masaki was...
- I-It's all right, Ryu!

00:05:30.927 --> 00:05:31.927
I'll be...

00:05:34.473 --> 00:05:35.473
Miss Masaki?

00:05:35.682 --> 00:05:36.682
Masaki!

00:05:38.476 --> 00:05:40.353
What's wrong?!
Are you in pain?

00:05:44.608 --> 00:05:45.608
No...!

00:05:46.442 --> 00:05:48.528
Is that... a Hollow's hole?

00:05:49.071 --> 00:05:51.112
What do you think you're doing,
Ryuken?

00:05:51.113 --> 00:05:52.031
Where's Father?!

00:05:52.033 --> 00:05:54.158
We're trying to get in touch
with him right now.

00:05:54.533 --> 00:05:55.576
You will wait here.

00:05:57.788 --> 00:05:58.788
Wait!

00:05:58.788 --> 00:06:01.247
You can't be with that thing!

00:06:01.249 --> 00:06:03.250
You'll put yourself in danger!

00:06:03.250 --> 00:06:04.336
Come back!

00:06:04.961 --> 00:06:05.920
Please...

00:06:05.922 --> 00:06:07.588
Come back, Ryuken!

00:06:15.012 --> 00:06:17.139
<i>What is this thing
that resembles a Hollow's hole?</i>

00:06:17.557 --> 00:06:19.434
<i>Why is she in so much pain?</i>

00:06:20.101 --> 00:06:21.769
<i>What's happening to Masaki?</i>

00:06:22.437 --> 00:06:25.021
<i>Why didn't I stop her by force?</i>

00:06:25.023 --> 00:06:28.901
<i>Why didn't I do everything I could
to interrupt that battle?</i>

00:06:29.860 --> 00:06:30.862
<i>Why?!</i>

00:06:40.038 --> 00:06:42.249
Whew, that was a close one!

00:06:42.540 --> 00:06:44.084
It almost got you!

00:06:44.875 --> 00:06:45.877
It's you!

00:06:47.045 --> 00:06:48.129
What's wrong?

00:06:51.507 --> 00:06:53.134
Wait, let me take a look at her!

00:06:53.384 --> 00:06:54.386
Don't touch her!

00:06:55.302 --> 00:06:58.139
Why do you think
this is happening to her?

00:06:58.848 --> 00:07:00.725
It's because she protected you!

00:07:02.435 --> 00:07:07.149
She broke the rules of the Quincies
to protect you, a Soul Reaper...

00:07:07.607 --> 00:07:09.483
And because of that,
she was wounded...

00:07:10.276 --> 00:07:12.987
Why does Masaki
have to go through this?!

00:07:14.822 --> 00:07:17.033
That wound is what's causing this?

00:07:17.576 --> 00:07:19.286
I can't think of
any other explanation.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:21.161
I'll never forgive you for...

00:07:21.163 --> 00:07:22.581
Let's stop right there.

00:07:24.915 --> 00:07:26.793
There's no time to argue.

00:07:27.543 --> 00:07:30.088
Please come with me, both of you.

00:07:31.088 --> 00:07:34.050
I'll tell you the choices
you have to save her...

00:07:57.281 --> 00:07:58.658
<i>I'm falling...</i>

00:07:59.951 --> 00:08:02.370
<i>Falling down a peaceful hole.</i>

00:08:04.331 --> 00:08:08.918
<i>It's quiet, dark and lonely...</i>

00:08:10.170 --> 00:08:12.379
<i>Yet, I'm not scared...</i>

00:08:13.507 --> 00:08:14.507
<i>I have this feeling...</i>

00:08:15.007 --> 00:08:18.427
<i>that someone who needs me
is waiting for me down there...</i>

00:08:20.846 --> 00:08:21.847
<i>Who's there?</i>

00:08:31.524 --> 00:08:33.442
"URAHARA'S SHOP"
I've been researching the same
symptom that she is exhibiting

00:08:33.442 --> 00:08:36.028
I've been researching the same
symptom that she is exhibiting

00:08:36.028 --> 00:08:38.072
for close to a hundred years.

00:08:38.532 --> 00:08:39.533
A hundred years?!

00:08:39.908 --> 00:08:41.408
Just who are you anyway?

00:08:42.076 --> 00:08:44.703
My name is Kisuke Urahara.

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.331
I was banished
from the Soul Society.

00:08:47.957 --> 00:08:49.917
<i>You're</i> Kisuke Urahara?

00:08:49.918 --> 00:08:52.086
I don't care who you are!

00:08:52.836 --> 00:08:54.589
Hurry up and restore Masaki
back to normal!

00:08:55.173 --> 00:08:57.413
I never said anything about
restoring her back to normal.

00:08:57.884 --> 00:08:58.884
What?

00:08:59.094 --> 00:09:00.333
I'll give it to you straight...

00:09:00.971 --> 00:09:02.096
That young lady...

00:09:02.846 --> 00:09:05.642
Masaki can never go back
to the way she used to be.

00:09:07.476 --> 00:09:09.937
Her condition
is known as Hollowfication.

00:09:11.022 --> 00:09:14.024
Hollowfication is what happens
when a Hollow's soul

00:09:14.024 --> 00:09:15.777
is poured into another soul,

00:09:16.152 --> 00:09:19.447
destroying the boundaries
between the two souls.

00:09:19.739 --> 00:09:24.076
It is the result of an attempt to
sublimate a soul to a higher level.

00:09:24.451 --> 00:09:28.123
Originally, it was meant to
strengthen a Soul Reaper's soul.

00:09:28.706 --> 00:09:30.874
However,
souls that undergo Hollowfication

00:09:30.875 --> 00:09:32.961
eventually become
mindless monsters,

00:09:33.378 --> 00:09:36.923
and ultimately self-destruct
against their will...

00:09:37.423 --> 00:09:39.049
a process known as Soul Suicide.

00:09:40.134 --> 00:09:42.721
Hollowfication is
an uncontrollable technology.

00:09:43.263 --> 00:09:44.888
Uncontrollable?!

00:09:44.889 --> 00:09:48.309
Doesn't that mean there's no way
to save Masaki?

00:09:49.019 --> 00:09:51.604
I can't return her
to the way she was,

00:09:51.605 --> 00:09:53.565
but I <i>can</i> save her life...

00:09:57.568 --> 00:10:00.113
During my research
over the past hundred years,

00:10:00.279 --> 00:10:03.616
I discovered a way to prevent
this Soul Suicide.

00:10:04.075 --> 00:10:06.869
It involves injecting something
into the victim's soul

00:10:06.870 --> 00:10:09.538
that can counteract Hollowfication...

00:10:10.206 --> 00:10:12.291
This allows the soul
to maintain balance

00:10:12.292 --> 00:10:14.336
so that their boundaries
won't get destroyed.

00:10:14.668 --> 00:10:16.796
Thus, preventing a Soul Suicide.

00:10:19.006 --> 00:10:20.407
Let me give you a specific example.

00:10:21.134 --> 00:10:23.677
If we inject
a Hollowfied Soul Reaper

00:10:23.677 --> 00:10:27.764
with a vaccine made from a Quincy's
light arrow and a human soul,

00:10:27.765 --> 00:10:30.601
they'll remain in
whatever state they're in.

00:10:31.436 --> 00:10:35.023
However, Quincies have
no resistance against Hollows,

00:10:35.649 --> 00:10:37.859
so the vaccine isn't enough...

00:10:38.025 --> 00:10:39.485
I don't understand what you mean.

00:10:39.860 --> 00:10:41.278
To put it in simpler terms,

00:10:41.863 --> 00:10:43.029
we're trying to neutralize it

00:10:43.030 --> 00:10:46.158
by hitting it
with a counteracting force.

00:10:46.701 --> 00:10:50.037
To save this Quincy girl's life,
prevent her Hollowfication

00:10:50.038 --> 00:10:53.041
while retaining
her existence as a human...

00:10:53.457 --> 00:10:56.961
we need a stronger
counteracting force.

00:10:57.921 --> 00:10:59.546
Something that must
remain by her side

00:10:59.547 --> 00:11:00.881
at all times until she dies...

00:11:01.006 --> 00:11:03.509
A powerful counteracting force

00:11:03.967 --> 00:11:06.136
that continues to suppress
her Hollowfication...

00:11:06.261 --> 00:11:07.263
You're lying!

00:11:08.097 --> 00:11:10.975
There must be some other way...!

00:11:12.143 --> 00:11:13.477
You're quite sharp.

00:11:13.937 --> 00:11:15.145
You quickly figured it out.

00:11:16.063 --> 00:11:19.067
However...
you have no choice in this matter...

00:11:19.984 --> 00:11:21.735
The one with a choice...

00:11:22.528 --> 00:11:24.322
is you, Isshin Shiba.

00:11:26.408 --> 00:11:29.076
Soul Reapers are
the opposites of Quincies...

00:11:29.410 --> 00:11:31.705
Humans are the opposites
of Hollows...

00:11:31.955 --> 00:11:36.125
Currently, Masaki is a hybrid
of a Quincy and a Hollow...

00:11:37.043 --> 00:11:38.753
To counteract that, we need...

00:11:39.211 --> 00:11:42.131
someone who is a hybrid
of Soul Reaper and human.

00:11:45.051 --> 00:11:47.136
This is a special Gigai I created...

00:11:47.721 --> 00:11:50.306
It was created from a human soul.

00:11:50.849 --> 00:11:53.392
It envelops the soul
that enters it,

00:11:53.393 --> 00:11:54.936
making them completely human.

00:11:56.437 --> 00:11:57.730
You understand now, don't you?

00:11:58.355 --> 00:12:02.610
If you use this, you'll become
a hybrid of Soul Reaper and human.

00:12:03.235 --> 00:12:06.822
Which means you can
become her opposite.

00:12:08.490 --> 00:12:10.909
<i>This</i> is the choice
I'm presenting to you.

00:12:11.535 --> 00:12:16.081
However, this choice has
far too many downsides for you.

00:12:16.750 --> 00:12:18.250
I must bind your soul

00:12:18.250 --> 00:12:22.546
to Masaki's soul
and the Hollow within her

00:12:22.547 --> 00:12:25.216
with a string of Reishi.

00:12:25.841 --> 00:12:28.427
For as long as Masaki lives...

00:12:28.761 --> 00:12:29.761
No...

00:12:29.763 --> 00:12:32.639
It will be forever passed down
to her descendants.

00:12:33.099 --> 00:12:34.975
While you are in this Gigai,

00:12:35.393 --> 00:12:38.187
not only will you be unable to
use your Soul Reaper powers,

00:12:38.730 --> 00:12:41.024
but you won't even
be able to see Hollows.

00:12:41.941 --> 00:12:44.693
And it's likely that
once you get in...

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:48.114
you'll never return to being
a Soul Reaper ever again...

00:12:51.158 --> 00:12:53.787
<i>This has only downsides for him!</i>

00:12:54.370 --> 00:12:56.370
<i>There's no way he would accept
something like this!</i>

00:12:56.873 --> 00:12:57.914
<i>He'd never—</i>

00:12:57.916 --> 00:12:59.583
Okay, I'll do it!

00:13:00.668 --> 00:13:02.794
- What?!
- I said I'll do it!

00:13:02.796 --> 00:13:03.879
Hurry up!

00:13:03.879 --> 00:13:05.923
Man, you talk too much!

00:13:06.131 --> 00:13:07.381
I have to quit being a Soul Reaper

00:13:07.383 --> 00:13:09.028
and protect her
for the rest of her life, right?!

00:13:09.052 --> 00:13:10.427
Of course, I'll do it!

00:13:11.971 --> 00:13:13.730
You're okay with giving up
your current life?

00:13:13.972 --> 00:13:15.432
Are you kidding me?

00:13:15.808 --> 00:13:16.809
Hell no!

00:13:17.601 --> 00:13:18.977
But so what?!

00:13:19.854 --> 00:13:21.480
If I let the person
who saved my life die

00:13:22.023 --> 00:13:23.857
because I couldn't make a decision...

00:13:24.274 --> 00:13:26.110
I know my future self
will laugh at me!

00:13:32.241 --> 00:13:33.241
Very well.

00:13:34.660 --> 00:13:36.120
I shall begin the procedure.

00:13:47.465 --> 00:13:48.466
Yo...

00:13:49.259 --> 00:13:51.009
I'm here to protect you.

00:13:55.139 --> 00:13:56.224
Hey, Hollow!

00:13:56.682 --> 00:13:58.057
Now that I'm here,

00:13:58.058 --> 00:14:01.019
I won't let you
lay a finger on her!

00:14:04.023 --> 00:14:07.192
Getsuga... Tensho!

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:24.918
I've successfully
connected your souls.

00:14:25.461 --> 00:14:26.837
She'll be all right now.

00:14:27.087 --> 00:14:28.089
I see...

00:14:28.464 --> 00:14:29.465
Thank goodness...

00:14:32.342 --> 00:14:36.054
You're that Soul Reaper
from the other day...

00:14:37.264 --> 00:14:40.100
Please tell me your name...!

00:14:42.102 --> 00:14:43.145
Thank goodness...

00:15:01.956 --> 00:15:04.292
Did you leave Miss Masaki behind...

00:15:05.083 --> 00:15:06.168
with the Soul Reaper?

00:15:08.046 --> 00:15:09.047
I did.

00:15:10.631 --> 00:15:12.549
Go home and tell my mother...

00:15:13.216 --> 00:15:16.888
that Ryuken is unqualified
to protect the Quincies.

00:15:17.764 --> 00:15:19.932
- No. I'm not leaving.
- I said go home.

00:15:20.432 --> 00:15:21.433
No.

00:15:22.018 --> 00:15:24.057
I will not leave you here
by yourself, Young Master.

00:15:24.144 --> 00:15:25.605
- Katagiri...!
- Master Ryuken...

00:15:25.938 --> 00:15:26.940
Have you forgotten?

00:15:28.149 --> 00:15:33.696
It is my duty to devote
my entire life to serving you.

00:15:35.405 --> 00:15:37.075
From the day I first met you,

00:15:37.951 --> 00:15:40.370
my life has belonged to you.

00:15:41.412 --> 00:15:42.621
So please...

00:15:43.456 --> 00:15:45.166
Please do not be sad.

00:15:47.751 --> 00:15:49.754
When you are sad,

00:15:50.797 --> 00:15:52.715
it tears my heart apart.

00:15:54.008 --> 00:15:55.509
When you cry...

00:15:55.509 --> 00:15:56.677
Katagiri...

00:15:57.971 --> 00:15:58.971
That's enough.

00:15:59.514 --> 00:16:00.514
Let's go home.

00:16:05.227 --> 00:16:08.398
Yes, understood, Young Master...

00:16:12.860 --> 00:16:16.197
<i>After that,
soon after graduating high school,</i>

00:16:16.822 --> 00:16:18.950
<i>Masaki left the Ishida family.</i>

00:16:19.826 --> 00:16:21.660
<i>Her soul was mixed with a Hollow.</i>

00:16:22.035 --> 00:16:24.831
<i>For the Quincies,
it was the proper decision...</i>

00:16:25.081 --> 00:16:26.706
"KUROSAKI CLINIC" <i>As for me,</i>

00:16:26.707 --> 00:16:28.947
<i>I made use of the medical skills
I learned at the Academy</i>

00:16:29.085 --> 00:16:30.919
<i>and opened up a small clinic.</i>

00:16:32.462 --> 00:16:34.590
<i>There were a ton of things
I had to learn,</i>

00:16:35.091 --> 00:16:38.094
<i>but with Urahara's help,
I somehow managed.</i>

00:16:39.011 --> 00:16:40.596
<i>When Masaki became
a college student,</i>

00:16:40.846 --> 00:16:43.099
<i>she would often come by
to make fun of my white coat.</i>

00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:47.477
<i>I told Masaki that I lost
my Soul Reaper powers</i>

00:16:47.894 --> 00:16:51.648
<i>because I was banished from
the Soul Society for screwing up.</i>

00:16:52.482 --> 00:16:58.530
<i>She probably saw through my lies
from the moment I told her that.</i>

00:16:59.281 --> 00:17:01.241
<i>I was terrible at lying</i>

00:17:01.951 --> 00:17:04.162
<i>and her intuition
was incredibly sharp.</i>

00:17:05.246 --> 00:17:10.876
<i>So lying to her felt trivial
and meaningless.</i>

00:17:12.002 --> 00:17:14.880
<i>She would always
see through my lies</i>

00:17:14.881 --> 00:17:17.133
<i>and forgive me for telling them...</i>

00:17:18.384 --> 00:17:21.220
<i>In a movie we saw together,</i>

00:17:21.887 --> 00:17:24.096
<i>an old man compared the old woman
he spent many years with</i>

00:17:24.097 --> 00:17:25.682
<i>to the sun.</i>

00:17:26.683 --> 00:17:29.019
<i>I don't remember
the rest of the movie</i>

00:17:29.269 --> 00:17:31.509
<i>aside from the fact that
it made Masaki burst into tears,</i>

00:17:31.855 --> 00:17:34.067
<i>but that one line stuck with me...</i>

00:17:35.151 --> 00:17:37.278
<i>Masaki was like the sun...</i>

00:17:38.653 --> 00:17:41.740
<i>She attracted everything,
forgave everything,</i>

00:17:42.032 --> 00:17:44.786
<i>illuminated everything,
and spun everything around...</i>

00:17:46.412 --> 00:17:47.413
<i>I was just...</i>

00:17:48.914 --> 00:17:52.210
<i>happy to be spun around by her.</i>

00:17:54.711 --> 00:17:55.712
<i>And then...</i>

00:17:56.213 --> 00:17:57.714
you were born.

00:17:58.965 --> 00:18:01.384
You already know the rest.

00:18:02.470 --> 00:18:05.309
By coming into contact with Rukia,
you gained your Soul Reaper powers...

00:18:05.932 --> 00:18:08.183
By training with Urahara,
you gained your Zanpakuto...

00:18:08.726 --> 00:18:11.854
And through your battles
in the Soul Society,

00:18:12.188 --> 00:18:14.648
the Hollow in you was awakened.

00:18:16.025 --> 00:18:21.113
The fact that it was released
means that my Soul Pressure

00:18:21.114 --> 00:18:23.449
was no longer able to suppress him.

00:18:24.200 --> 00:18:28.538
And so, my connection to my Gigai
and that Hollow was broken.

00:18:29.122 --> 00:18:31.038
That's how I regained
my Soul Reaper powers

00:18:31.039 --> 00:18:32.375
for the first time in 20 years.

00:18:33.416 --> 00:18:37.505
I probably don't need to explain
the things you already experienced.

00:18:38.588 --> 00:18:39.589
But...

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:42.468
there is still one thing
that you've experienced

00:18:43.051 --> 00:18:44.846
that you don't know
the whole story about.

00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:47.097
Nine years ago from today...

00:18:47.557 --> 00:18:48.932
June 17th...

00:18:49.933 --> 00:18:51.894
The day your mom died.

00:18:53.938 --> 00:18:54.939
You need to know...

00:18:56.022 --> 00:19:00.486
the real reason
your mom died that day...

00:19:08.536 --> 00:19:11.497
<i>Everything we had left behind</i>

00:19:11.663 --> 00:19:16.001
<i>Our breaths blending as mist</i>

00:19:16.126 --> 00:19:20.298
<i>without form or expression</i>

00:19:20.423 --> 00:19:24.594
<i>We lie buried as we glare
into the distance</i>

00:19:24.926 --> 00:19:27.555
<i>I can't hear anything</i>

00:19:27.680 --> 00:19:30.807
<i>I can't seem to cut anything</i>

00:19:30.932 --> 00:19:33.310
<i>It feels like I'm sinking</i>

00:19:33.435 --> 00:19:35.269
<i>Falling, falling</i>

00:19:35.270 --> 00:19:36.355
<i>Touching</i>

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:39.857
<i>Eyes struck wide open</i>

00:19:39.858 --> 00:19:43.195
<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:19:43.320 --> 00:19:49.492
<i>The furthest reaches are now visible to us</i>

00:19:49.868 --> 00:19:53.455
<i>It cannot be undone
and cannot be stopped</i>

00:19:53.580 --> 00:19:56.916
<i>This ensuing struggle</i>

00:19:56.917 --> 00:20:01.797
<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:20:01.923 --> 00:20:03.965
<i>Along with our breaths</i>

00:20:04.174 --> 00:20:05.467
<i>Take everything</i>

00:20:05.468 --> 00:20:10.222
<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:20:10.347 --> 00:20:12.266
<i>Along with our futures</i>

00:20:12.391 --> 00:20:14.143
<i>Along with our world</i>

00:20:15.228 --> 00:20:18.480
<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:20:18.605 --> 00:20:24.861
<i>The furthest reaches are now
visible to us</i>

00:20:24.862 --> 00:20:26.948
<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:20:27.073 --> 00:20:28.865
<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:20:28.990 --> 00:20:32.327
<i>As we tear each other down</i>

00:20:35.705 --> 00:20:36.707
Your mom...

00:20:37.250 --> 00:20:40.044
She wasn't supposed to
die that day...

00:20:40.961 --> 00:20:42.003
What do you mean?

00:20:44.048 --> 00:20:45.048
Your mom...

00:20:45.633 --> 00:20:46.634
Masaki...

00:20:47.134 --> 00:20:48.885
Even though she had merged
with a Hollow,

00:20:49.511 --> 00:20:51.596
she was originally an Echt Quincy.

00:20:52.265 --> 00:20:55.767
Her defensive ability,
the Blut Vene,

00:20:55.768 --> 00:20:57.728
was exceptionally powerful.

00:20:59.230 --> 00:21:01.147
Not only could she defeat
Grand Fisher,

00:21:01.773 --> 00:21:06.069
but she could have done it without
getting a single scratch on her.

00:21:06.569 --> 00:21:07.570
However...

00:21:16.038 --> 00:21:17.789
That didn't happen...

00:21:18.708 --> 00:21:19.708
Why not?

00:21:19.709 --> 00:21:22.920
It's because she lost
her Quincy powers that day...

00:21:23.045 --> 00:21:24.046
But how?!

00:21:24.880 --> 00:21:27.048
What happened... nine years ago?!

00:21:28.092 --> 00:21:29.134
Auswählen.

00:21:29.468 --> 00:21:31.429
AUSWÄHLEN

00:21:32.054 --> 00:21:35.473
It's a Quincy selection process
conducted by Yhwach himself.

00:21:37.684 --> 00:21:39.394
I heard of a Quincy tale

00:21:39.394 --> 00:21:42.315
that sang praises of a king
who was sealed away.

00:21:43.231 --> 00:21:44.317
According to that,

00:21:45.151 --> 00:21:49.529
The confined Quincy King
regains his pulse after 900 years.

00:21:49.904 --> 00:21:52.199
His mind after 90 years.

00:21:52.700 --> 00:21:55.036
His strength after 9 years.

00:21:55.952 --> 00:22:01.875
Yhwach robbed Quincies
he deemed impure of their powers

00:22:01.875 --> 00:22:03.919
and made them his own.

00:22:04.461 --> 00:22:05.587
As a result...

00:22:06.005 --> 00:22:11.259
Uryu's frail mother,
Kanae Katagiri, lost her life...

00:22:11.926 --> 00:22:17.016
And how Masaki lost her powers
and lost her life in battle...

00:22:17.724 --> 00:22:18.726
How?

00:22:19.059 --> 00:22:20.935
How is he able to do that?

00:22:21.770 --> 00:22:22.971
Is it because he's their king?

00:22:23.146 --> 00:22:24.940
Who is Yhwach anyway?!

00:22:27.276 --> 00:22:30.278
Yhwach is the Father
of the Quincies.

00:22:31.113 --> 00:22:33.115
The Quincies started from him...

00:22:33.531 --> 00:22:38.412
And all Quincies have his blood
running in their veins.

00:22:39.622 --> 00:22:42.874
<i>The memories within
your Spiritual Pressure</i>

00:22:42.875 --> 00:22:44.875
<i>have awakened too soon.</i>

00:22:44.876 --> 00:22:47.753
<i>It is unable to contain Quincies!</i>

00:22:47.755 --> 00:22:51.008
<i>You don't know anything
about yourself, do you?</i>

00:22:51.509 --> 00:22:55.054
<i>Not even about... your own mother.</i>

00:22:57.097 --> 00:22:59.974
<i>Farewell, Ichigo Kurosaki...</i>

00:23:00.893 --> 00:23:04.939
<i>my son... born in the dark...</i>

00:23:08.776 --> 00:23:09.777
Dad...

00:23:11.987 --> 00:23:12.988
Thanks.

00:23:18.035 --> 00:23:19.035
No problem.

00:23:26.167 --> 00:23:27.294
Hey, Ichigo...

00:23:30.506 --> 00:23:34.093
You forgot this...
I came to deliver it to you.

00:23:41.016 --> 00:23:42.977
Thanks, Ms. Ikumi.

00:23:45.354 --> 00:23:46.355
Dad...

00:23:49.692 --> 00:23:51.317
I'm going.

00:23:56.740 --> 00:24:00.577
<i>"I believe the world
is full of danger."</i>

00:24:00.702 --> 00:24:03.913
<i>"I want to protect you from it."</i>

00:24:04.248 --> 00:24:10.128
<i>"Only because inside me is
the same impulse as that danger."</i>

